    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine is currently overheating within minutes of starting, and there is a heavy clunking sound coming from the transmission when shifting into gear. Additionally, the body has significant rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn. It will need to be towed from its current location as it is not roadworthy.",
